comment._content:
This AC is another Me-262A-1a Swallow  JF(2)  Ger WWII
this AC claims wn 500443 and is marked Yellow 5
the location where shown is at an Air Show in Germany I believe, though could be wrong on that.  This AC was reported to have been assembled from more that one other AC, Privately held, and resides in Germany.
